---
import SiteLayout from "../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
---
<SiteLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for PoE2 Hub, covering how Google Analytics and Google AdSense collect and use data on this site."
>
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="updated-note">Last updated: July 10, 2026</p>

  <h2>Introduction</h2>
  <p>
    This Privacy Policy explains how PoE2 Hub (<a href="https://poe2hub.net">https://poe2hub.net</a>)
    handles information when you visit the site. We built PoE2 Hub as a straightforward guide
    resource, and this policy is written to be just as straightforward about what data is
    collected and why.
  </p>

  <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>
    PoE2 Hub does not directly ask you to create an account or submit personal information to
    use the site. However, the third-party services we use, Google Analytics and Google AdSense,
    may automatically collect certain data as described below.
  </p>

  <h2>Google Analytics</h2>
  <p>
    We use Google Analytics (Measurement ID: <code>G-BE38KVGCF3</code>) to understand how
    visitors use the site, which pages get read, how people navigate between them, and general
    usage patterns. This data is collected anonymously and in aggregate, we don't use it to
    identify individual visitors. Google Analytics uses cookies to distinguish separate site
    visits. You can learn more about how Google handles this data at
    <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google's Privacy & Terms page</a>.
  </p>

  <h2>Google AdSense</h2>
  <p>
    PoE2 Hub uses Google AdSense to display advertising. Google and its partners use cookies to
    serve ads based on your prior visits to this site and other sites on the internet. You can
    opt out of personalized advertising by visiting
    <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google's Ads Settings</a>,
    or by visiting <a href="https://www.aboutads.info/choices/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">www.aboutads.info</a>
    if you'd prefer to opt out of third-party vendor use of cookies for personalized advertising
    more broadly.
  </p>

  <h2>Cookies</h2>
  <p>This site uses two categories of cookies:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Analytics cookies</strong> (via Google Analytics), used to understand site traffic and usage patterns.</li>
    <li><strong>Advertising cookies</strong> (via Google AdSense), used to serve and measure ads, including personalized ads based on your browsing activity.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    You can control or delete cookies through your browser settings at any time. Disabling
    cookies may affect how ads are displayed but won't prevent you from reading site content.
  </p>

  <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>PoE2 Hub uses the following third-party services, each with its own privacy policy governing how it handles data:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Analytics</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google AdSense</a></li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Data Retention</h2>
  <p>
    We don't independently store personal data submitted through the site, since there's no
    account system or data submission form. Data collected by Google Analytics and Google
    AdSense is retained according to Google's own retention policies, which you can review
    through the links above.
  </p>

  <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>
    PoE2 Hub is not directed at children under the age of 13, and we do not knowingly collect
    personal information from children under 13.
  </p>

  <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>
    We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or
    for legal and regulatory reasons. Updates will be posted on this page with a revised "Last
    updated" date.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact Us</h2>
  <p>
    Questions about this Privacy Policy: <a href="mailto:cdomiy@gmail.com">cdomiy@gmail.com</a>
  </p>
</SiteLayout>

<style>
  .updated-note { color: var(--text-faint); font-size: 0.88rem; }
  h2 { margin-top: var(--space-3); }
  p { color: var(--text-dim); line-height: 1.75; }
  ul { color: var(--text-dim); padding-left: 1.2em; }
  li { margin-bottom: 0.4em; }
</style>
